  {color:#172B4D}*Dear Team,*{color} 
{color:#172B4D} I’m thrilled to share a landmark moment in our journey together:  _we have officially issued our first annuity._{color} 
{color:#172B4D} This is a testament to the collective passion, intelligence, and relentless execution each of you brings to our mission. Every bit of work—from strategy and ops to product, engineering, and customer care—has contributed to making this possible.{color} 
{color:#172B4D} Getting to this point hasn’t been easy, and that’s what makes it so rewarding. It’s proof that our vision is working, that our platform is resonating, and most importantly, that  _we're just getting started_.{color} 
{color:#172B4D} On behalf of the entire leadership team, thank you—and congratulations. Let’s take a moment to celebrate this achievement, and then get ready for the many more that are ahead.{color} 
{color:#172B4D} With gratitude,{color} 
{color:#172B4D} Deanna{color}{color:#172B4D}{color}{color:#172B4D}{color} 
